3c8862ef4fd32093507b91381fcfa4","tid":2365301,"uid":223428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:45:07.000Z","msg":"德國在1919年威瑪共和時期非常動盪。由於要在國會大廈獲得席次沒有訂定選舉門檻，要獲得席次有可能僅需有0.4%的選票即可。這導致大量的政黨獲得席次，讓政府難以維持多數派，而聯合政府亦經常遭倒閣。戰後，在國會獲得席次訂定選舉門檻，要獲得席次需有5%的選票，並採取「建設性不信任投票」，以防止頻繫的倒閣。"},{"pid":"e0bfceb1a5fe6f2a6d48a806ba67b8f5d8924df9","tid":2365301,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/80/Jap_festival_hk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F8%2F80%2FJap_festival_hk.jpg&h=fa684193&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49558938d354a93381d992544aba3087a81c8f30","tid":2365301,"uid":302184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:49:21.000Z","msg":"你老母我忍夠 鴻圖道係荒謬"},{"pid":"3a73cd1562182fcf01e9102503d4946b3a09f170","tid":2365301,"uid":233156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:53:04.000Z","msg":"猶如在夢幻國　神奇力量贈我<br />\n袋仔的法寶<br />\n<br />\n同遊萬象太空　銀河上面捕捉<br />\n光陰的美好<br />\n<br />\n難題若是遇到　隨時隨地就變身<br />\n彷彿滿腹靈感<br />\n<br />\n快飛往怡神無愁樂國<br />\n挽手跟星光閃閃跳舞<br />\n<br />\n隨意踏進這扇門<br />\n讓理想得到夢變真<br />\n越過鐵路和郊野<br />\n轉眼再現夢快車<br />\n<br />\nSha la la la la<br />\n陪伴我一起歌唱<br />\n高聲安歌　同樂去踏踏步<br />\nDoraemon 讓此刻不會老　夢境終可以達到<br />\n<br />\nSha la la la la<br />\n陪伴我一起歌唱<br />\n高聲安歌　同樂去踏踏步<br />\nDoraemon　讓此刻不會老　美景將可以望見得到"},{"pid":"103bc1f97cc79779fb48e012aa3ff10fad499228","tid":2365301,"uid":305631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:55:36.000Z","msg":"笑咗 點解個肚咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d9b02d1f7ccae10befa1b2b3c2df083e1629f5","tid":2365301,"uid":255581,"lik